JUnititorial Services at Nappan Farm
=====================================

**Tender Notice**
---------------

Tender 01B46-23-124

The Department of Agriculture and Agri-Food Canada (AAFC) invites bidders to submit proposals for the provision of janitorial services at Nappan Farm in Kentville, Nova Scotia.

**Procurement Overview**
------------------------

The successful Bidder will be required to provide cleaning services for AAFC's buildings in accordance with the specifications outlined in this document.

**Mandatory Site Visit**
------------------------

A mandatory Site Visit is scheduled to take place on November 29, 2023, at 11:00 am AST. Interested Bidders must attend this visit and sign in with the Commissionaire at Building 10, 4016 Hwy 302, Nappan, NS B0L 1C0.

**Tender Period Closing Date and Time**
-----------------------------------------

The Tender Period closing date and time is December 13, 2023, at 2:00 pm EST. All Proposals must be submitted electronically to aafc.escprocurement-cseapprovisionnement.aac@agr.gc.ca.

**Important Notes**
------------------

*   The Bidder shall ensure that their Proposal is submitted on time and in accordance with the instructions outlined in this document.
*   AAFC reserves the right to accept any Proposal in whole or in part, without prior negotiation, and to reject any or all Proposals.
*   The Bidder shall not contact anyone other than the AAFC Contract Officer for information related to this Tender Process.

**Tender Documents**
---------------------

All Tender Documents, including the specifications, plans, and drawings, are available on the BuyandSell service provider's platform. Addenda will be issued in the same manner and will be available on the platform.

**Contracting Officer**
-----------------------

For any questions or concerns related to this Tender Process, please contact the AAFC Contract Officer, Carol Rahal, at:
*   Address: 2001 Robert-Bourassa, Room 671-TEN, Montreal, QC H3A 3N2
*   Phone: (514) 231-3209
*   Email: [carol.rahal@agr.gc.ca](mailto:carol.rahal@agr.gc.ca)

**Tender Attachments**
----------------------

Attachments for this Tender Notice are available at: <https://canadabuys.canada.ca/sites/default/files/webform/tender.notice/22725/added
